-- Speech-tag palette generated by the outline LLM and reused by the
-- chapter LLM as inline X.ai TTS tags. Examples: "[pause]", "[laugh]",
-- "<whisper>", "<soft>", "<slow>". The chapter generator embeds these
-- inline in `chapter.body_md`; the X.ai TTS endpoint consumes them
-- directly from the text. Stored on the book so the same palette is
-- applied across all chapters and translations.
--
-- See https://docs.x.ai/developers/model-capabilities/audio/text-to-speech#speech-tags

DEFINE FIELD IF NOT EXISTS tags ON audiobook TYPE array<string> DEFAULT [];
